	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Aug 6th 1:45 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay folks, after being a melee or cleric type for six months, I'm venturing into the realm of casters and I'm fairly clueless. Any advice and help would be very appreciated.<br><br>1. Pets: Is Highhold Keep the only place to get 8th and 12th level pet spells? If so, from whom do you get them? What a hassle!<br><br>2. I've tried using the pet commands in the EQ book, even made hotkeys, but the pets seem to ignore them. Am I missing something?<br><br>3. Any great way to target and mez adds in a fight? I have a heck of a time in small spaces trying to mez those adds that crowd around the melee types. Any hints?<br><br>Thanks in advance!<br>&nbsp;<br>Tenser - Mighty Enchanter<br>Hasan - The Erudite Paladin</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
